genresAdvancedInfo.name: musica queretana
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Musica Queretana is a traditional Mexican genre that originated in the state of Queretaro. It is characterized by the use of stringed instruments such as the guitar, vihuela, and guitarron, as well as the distinctive voice of the lead singer. The lyrics often focus on love, nature, and the beauty of the state's landscape.
